<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.9">
<l>atiruṅ kaṭalniṟa vaṇṇaṉai yāycci</l>
<l>matura mulaiyūṭṭi vañcittu vaittu</l>
<l>pataṟap paṭāmē paḻantāmpā lārtta</l>
<l>vutara miruntavā kāṇīrē yoḷivaḷai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with bright bangles, see the quality of the stomach</l>
<l>that was bound with an old rope,</l>
<l>[when] the cowherdess deceived and detained [him],</l>
<l>being unable to rush [around], she fed from [her] sweet breast</l>
<l>the one has the colour of the thundering sea. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
